Package: tardiff
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, xserver-xorg-input-evdev
Description: A tool to create binary differences between files.
 It takes to files and generate a diff file.
 It allows from first file and diff file to generate second one.